CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE [dbo].[ext_DIM_INVENTTABLE] WITH (
        LOCATION = 'DIM_INVENTTABLE/Archive',
        DATA_SOURCE = [eds_tx-halfen-2-dwh],
        FILE_FORMAT = [eff_Parquet] 
) AS
SELECT
    *
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK './DIM_INVENTTABLE/DIM_INVENTTABLE.csv',
        DATA_SOURCE = 'eds_tx-halfen-2-dwh',
        FORMAT = 'CSV', parser_version = '2.0',
        FIELDTERMINATOR =';',
        ROWTERMINATOR = '\r',
        HEADER_ROW = TRUE
    ) 
WITH (
    [DW_Id] bigint ,
	[ITEMID] VARCHAR (20) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	[ITEMGROUPID] VARCHAR (20) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	[ITEMNAME]VARCHAR (140) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	[DATAAREAID] VARCHAR (4) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	[HALPRODUCTLINEID] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	[ITEMTYPE] bigint ,
	[STOPEXPLODE] bigint ,
	[HALITEMTYPE_NAME] VARCHAR (1999) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	[HALITEMTYPE] bigint ,
	[ITEMTYPE_NAME] NVARCHAR (1999) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	[HPLBUSINESSRULESTATUSID] VARCHAR (30) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	[bomlines] bigint ,
	[HALISKIT] VARCHAR (50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	[HALPRODUCTRANGEID] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	[PRIMARYVENDORID] VARCHAR (20) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	[REQGROUPID] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	[HALSALEABLEITEM] bigint ,
	[HPLMAINSTATISTICGROUPID] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	[COSTGROUPID] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	[HALSurchargeGroupPURCH] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	[ITEMBUYERGROUPID] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
    [NETWEIGHT] decimal(38, 12) ,
	[StockUnit] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
    [MODELGROUPID] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
    [ADMIN_VirtualDataAreaid_INVENTMODELGROUP] VARCHAR (4) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
    [MODELGROUP_NAME] VARCHAR (140) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
    [INCLPHYSICALVALUEINCOST] BIGINT,
    [BOMUNITID] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
    [HALSTATISTICGROUPID] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	[HALPURCHCLASSIFIERID] VARCHAR (25) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
    [LastYear] bigint,
    [Type4PriceLastYear] decimal(38, 12),
	[PurchasePriceUnit] decimal(38, 12),
    [PurchPriceUnitID] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
    [Price_ForInventoryReporting] decimal(38, 12),
    [EXCHRATE_EUR] decimal(38, 12) ,
	[Type4PriceLastYear_EUR] decimal(38, 2) ,
	[HALPRODUCTLINENAME] VARCHAR (60) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	[HALPRODUCTLINEID_NAME] VARCHAR (100) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	[HALPRODUCTRANGENAME] VARCHAR (60) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	[HALPRODUCTRANGEID_NAME] VARCHAR (100) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	[HPLMAINSTATISTICGROUPNAME] VARCHAR (60) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,

	[HALSTATISTICGROUPNAME] VARCHAR (60) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,

	[HPLSTATISTICGROUPID] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	[HPLSTATISTICGROUPNAME] VARCHAR (60) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	[HPLSTATITICGROUPID_NAME] VARCHAR (100) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	[ITEMID_NAME] VARCHAR (120) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	[Type4MarkupLastYear] decimal(38, 12),
	[Type4PriceUnitLastYear] decimal(38, 12),
	[Type4PriceQuantityLastYear] decimal(38, 12),
	[INTRACODE] VARCHAR (10) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	[INTRACODENAME] VARCHAR (250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
	[INTRACODE_NAME] VARCHAR (200) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
